Available options for godi.conf:
 
- GODI_BASEPKG_EXPAT: Whether to build GODI's version of libexpat
  (yes/no). Defaults to "no".
 
- GODI_EXPAT_INCDIR: Where expat.h can be found. Set this option
  if GODI_BASEPKG_EXPAT=no, and the already installed expat
  library is not found.
 
- GODI_EXPAT_LIBDIR: Where libexpat can be found. Set this option
  if GODI_BASEPKG_EXPAT=no, and the already installed expat
  library is not found.
